    "updated_at": "2017-08-20T15:39:33Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Based on the discussion, I made a few changes:\r\n- logging is off by default, but when GRPC_VERBOSITY env variable is set, logging to stderr is enabled and log level is set accordingly.\r\n- added a LogLevel.Off  to LogLevel enum\r\n- unified the use of loggers in Grpc's test & benchmarks.\r\n\r\nPTAL"
